item.title: CVE-2021-24959|2024-08-03T19:49:13.934Z -- unknown -- wp%20email%20users
item.description: The WP Email Users WordPress plugin through 1.7.6 does not escape the data_raw parameter in the weu_selected_users_1 AJAX action, available to any authenticated users, allowing them to perform SQL injection attacks.
